{"tid":2020504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藤井莉娜自爆未婚懷孕　經手人係高中舊同學：我哋唔會註冊","createTime":"2020-05-17T06:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T06:34:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e404fd8c8fc78d250754cf826edba8759ae8bc1","tid":2020504,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"35歲日本模特兒藤井莉娜近年轉戰內地發展，更開設淘寶網店，撈得風山水起，有指年收入達2億港元，之前亦因為曾與尊尼事務所男星赤西仁、錦戶亮以及台灣男星江東城傳緋聞而備受關注。昨日（16/5），她在社交網站投出震撼彈，宣布公布未婚懷孕，BB爸爸是高中舊同學，但兩人不會結婚：「在這樣的時期，雖然有很不安，但想到腹中的小生命，便感到滿是幸福，我也希望與大家一起度過。」"},{"pid":"42083dcc27bbf631027ae8b57ead9239b46dc5e6","tid":2020504,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4503016/org/242e3610338bd7301ed995e88a089ea9.jpg/-T-GqQU3phA4AlAUIxgdmo8-TDbkVMM8-OFTg_jhU4M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4503016%2Forg%2F242e3610338bd7301ed995e88a089ea9.jpg%2F-T-GqQU3phA4AlAUIxgdmo8-TDbkVMM8-OFTg_jhU4M&h=b8d19103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4502997/org/053b53b2d38592fca2f72836359af740.jpg/Aewcrtbt-OzNPVqftlmq5tnC21U6LCZFQd4waUHeMGk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4502997%2Forg%2F053b53b2d38592fca2f72836359af740.jpg%2FAewcrtbt-OzNPVqftlmq5tnC21U6LCZFQd4waUHeMGk&h=fd55c4fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4502998/org/86abdb88d90d71f49a9f77f52b751064.jpg/HVyCqfqXeCRbgyFDg0-YfbhZoSmeuh3nHpoZsR6aGbE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4502998%2Forg%2F86abdb88d90d71f49a9f77f52b751064.jpg%2FHVyCqfqXeCRbgyFDg0-YfbhZoSmeuh3nHpoZsR6aGbE&h=a4cd5aab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed223a2829aa053a010b863ea95caef3a3c59a43","tid":2020504,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T06:18:04